Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.25,0:00:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The deal is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.50,0:00:19.21,jap-ja,,0,0,0,,交渉決裂だな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.71,0:00:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that there is much point in telling you now.
