Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.65,0:00:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,so I may have done that for a split second.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:00:53.95,jap-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに一瞬そうしたかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.62,0:00:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But what could I say when\NI'm merely the boss' chauffeur?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.68,0:00:55.56,jap-ja,,0,0,0,,だからって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.65,0:00:58.49,jap-ja,,0,0,0,,ボスの方針に　運転手の俺が何を言えるってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.22,0:01:00.97,jap-ja,,0,0,0,,やばい殺される
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.32,0:01:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap, I'm going to die!
